CatDescriptText: Cutline of possible related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 13, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "Nocturne - Stepping out in traditional style, the AKA Sorority, Iota Chapter, sponsored its annual Autumn Nocturne for freshmen and other members of the student body at Pitt, Saturday, Oct. 6. - Courier Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Two men, including one on left wearing military uniform, and five women posed behind table with punch bowl, including Mary Jane Mitchell Page on right, in Ammon Center gymnasium with curtain decorated with leaves, possibly for Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority Autumn Nocturne dance
